text: Ani he majhya janasamuhacya lokanno! Ata tumhi apalya thikani kama karita raha, midekhila kama karita ahe. Lavakaraca tumhala mahita padela ki konakade to azaba yeto, jo tyala apamanita karuna takila ani asa kona ahe jo khota ahe? Tumhi pratiksa kara ani midekhila tumacyasobata pratiksa karita ahe
